## 📦 Dependencies

| Library       | Purpose                        | Installation |
|---------------|--------------------------------|--------------|
| `tkinter`     | GUI framework                  | Built-in     |
| `re`          | Regular expressions            | Built-in     |
| `math`        | TF-IDF calculations            | Built-in     |
| `json`        | Knowledge base storage         | Built-in     |
| `os`          | File handling                  | Built-in     |
| `random`      | Response variation             | Built-in     |
| `time`        | Timestamps                     | Built-in     |
| `collections` | Counter, defaultdict for NLP   | Built-in     |

> **No external packages required.**

