## 💬 Sample Queries to Try

| You type...                        | Bot does...                              |
|------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| `hello`                            | Greeting response                        |
| `what are your business hours?`    | Returns hours from knowledge base        |
| `how do I return my laptop?`       | Return + refund policy                   |
| `where is my order #12345?`        | Tracks order by number                   |
| `how much does a smartphone cost?` | Retrieves pricing info                   |
| `my device is broken`              | Technical support + troubleshooting      |
| `I want to speak to a human`       | Escalates to human agent                 |
| `thank you`                        | Friendly farewell                        |

---

## 🛠️ Troubleshooting

**Tkinter not found on Windows?**
- Uninstall Python and reinstall from [python.org](https://python.org)
- During install, make sure **"tcl/tk and IDLE"** is checked

**Python not recognized in terminal?**
- Add Python to PATH during installation
- Or use: `py chatbot.py` instead of `python`

